=Lust and Lies=

00:00:40.399 --> 00:00:40.840
Qingwan.

00:00:44.719 --> 00:00:45.190
I bought these

00:00:45.600 --> 00:00:46.679
because I thought you'd like them.

00:00:47.159 --> 00:00:47.600
Take a look.

00:00:57.039 --> 00:00:58.000
I'll marry you.

00:01:02.799 --> 00:01:03.200
Really?

00:01:09.280 --> 00:01:12.200
Huo Xiu and I are over.

00:01:12.719 --> 00:01:14.000
You finally agreed to marry me.

00:01:14.200 --> 00:01:15.480
Let my aunt go!

00:01:18.760 --> 00:01:19.599
What's she doing here?

00:01:20.640 --> 00:01:22.120
When I saw her in that state,

00:01:22.840 --> 00:01:23.840
I brought her back.

00:01:30.079 --> 00:01:31.200
Pretending to be crazy, are you?

00:01:32.319 --> 00:01:33.319
Let her stay.

00:01:34.040 --> 00:01:36.640
She's the only family I have left.

00:01:43.400 --> 00:01:43.760
All right.

00:01:44.719 --> 00:01:46.239
Well, you should get some rest.

00:01:54.079 --> 00:01:54.879
Aunt.

00:02:00.239 --> 00:02:02.239
Yiyi, put this away for me.

00:02:02.920 --> 00:02:03.599
Okay.

00:02:18.680 --> 00:02:19.360
Huo Xiu.

00:02:21.480 --> 00:02:22.600
You left something behind again.

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:29.380
I came to return it
to its rightful owner.

00:02:51.940 --> 00:02:53.900
=Episode 23=

00:03:01.000 --> 00:03:04.439
Now, whoever marries Huo Qingwan

00:03:04.759 --> 00:03:06.680
will control the Huo Army

00:03:07.199 --> 00:03:09.120
and become the Governor of Sucheng.

00:03:14.759 --> 00:03:17.800
Do you think that if she found out
everything you've done,

00:03:18.759 --> 00:03:20.439
she'd still marry you?

00:03:22.360 --> 00:03:23.199
I want

00:03:24.439 --> 00:03:25.680
half of Sucheng.

00:03:29.520 --> 00:03:30.719
You've lost all your worth.

00:03:31.599 --> 00:03:32.960
What do you even have
to bargain with me?

00:03:37.319 --> 00:03:39.360
What if it's your life at stake?

00:03:40.120 --> 00:03:40.500
All right.

00:03:41.000 --> 00:03:41.759
I'll agree to your terms.

00:03:42.680 --> 00:03:43.159
Don't kill me.

00:03:48.759 --> 00:03:50.400
You're just like your father.

00:03:50.560 --> 00:03:52.879
An absolute coward.

00:04:02.919 --> 00:04:04.199
Has anyone ever told you

00:04:04.599 --> 00:04:05.639
that you talk too much?

00:04:07.439 --> 00:04:09.120
Qingwan wanted to spare you,

00:04:11.240 --> 00:04:12.199
but I think

00:04:13.520 --> 00:04:15.199
you're better off dead.

00:04:25.000 --> 00:04:28.199
Didn't we agree that after we succeeded
in taking revenge,

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:29.759
you'd marry me

00:04:30.879 --> 00:04:32.160
and we'd leave Sucheng together?

00:04:35.759 --> 00:04:37.800
I joined the Huo family for revenge.

00:04:38.879 --> 00:04:40.079
You don't actually think

00:04:41.519 --> 00:04:42.959
I've fallen for you, do you?

00:04:46.000 --> 00:04:47.000
It's best for us

00:04:47.439 --> 00:04:50.480
to part on good terms.

00:05:00.279 --> 00:05:01.360
Part on good terms?

00:05:02.759 --> 00:05:03.480
I refuse.

00:05:20.400 --> 00:05:21.199
Have you lost your mind?

00:05:22.439 --> 00:05:23.399
This is the Sheng Residence.

00:05:24.120 --> 00:05:25.120
I'm the Sheng family's bride.

00:05:29.439 --> 00:05:30.839
Then, let him see us like this.

00:05:32.079 --> 00:05:33.199
You're going to marry him?

00:05:34.600 --> 00:05:35.959
Well, who is his future bride

00:05:37.199 --> 00:05:38.720
in the arms of right now?

00:05:43.319 --> 00:05:44.000
What are you doing?

00:05:45.060 --> 00:05:50.700
♪It was just a single glance♪

00:05:51.439 --> 00:05:52.000
Huo Xiu!

