♪Sweet words exist only in dreams♪

00:06:05.380 --> 00:06:09.620
♪Memories are like faded negatives♪

00:06:09.620 --> 00:06:12.300
♪Replaying endlessly♪

00:06:12.300 --> 00:06:18.740
♪I turn around, but you are gone♪

00:06:18.900 --> 00:06:22.100
♪A moment apart feels
like endless years♪

00:06:22.100 --> 00:06:26.300
♪Amidst the light and shadow♪

