♪Why let ourselves fall deeper
than we already are?♪

00:06:32.240 --> 00:06:32.680
Huo Xiu!

00:06:32.920 --> 00:06:33.399
Huo Xiu!

00:06:35.399 --> 00:06:35.759
I…

00:06:35.959 --> 00:06:37.120
I'm Huo Qingwan!

00:06:44.519 --> 00:06:45.480
My father

00:06:46.879 --> 00:06:48.360
massacred the entire Gu family.

00:06:50.160 --> 00:06:50.839
And you

00:06:52.879 --> 00:06:54.759
killed my parents.

00:06:57.519 --> 00:07:00.000
How could we ever be together?

