♪It's you in the blur
of light and shadow♪

00:07:07.180 --> 00:07:13.060
♪Our first encounter
left me in awe for a lifetime♪

00:07:14.060 --> 00:07:18.060
♪Feelings I can't shake off♪

00:07:18.060 --> 00:07:20.540
♪Quietly emerge♪

00:07:21.680 --> 00:07:22.600
I don't believe it.

00:07:22.600 --> 00:07:26.620
♪It was just a single glance♪

