I didn't believe it

00:07:45.800 --> 00:07:46.639
at first,

00:07:48.639 --> 00:07:49.800
but I've regained

00:07:51.879 --> 00:07:52.839
all my past memories.

00:07:54.820 --> 00:07:58.060
♪A moment apart feels
like endless years♪

00:07:58.060 --> 00:08:01.740
♪Amidst the light and shadow♪

00:08:02.160 --> 00:08:03.079
Even so,

00:08:04.839 --> 00:08:06.439
I won't let you marry Sheng Weilian.

00:08:08.740 --> 00:08:11.780
♪Time can't outlast
a heart that remembers♪

00:08:11.780 --> 00:08:16.140
♪The past has already found its peace♪

00:08:16.140 --> 00:08:17.860
♪You remain the same♪

