Peace year after year.

00:11:07.399 --> 00:11:08.440
The ceremony

00:11:08.639 --> 00:11:09.480
will begin now.

00:11:11.519 --> 00:11:14.840
First, bow to Heaven and Earth.

00:11:30.200 --> 00:11:33.000
Second, bow to the elders.

00:11:39.360 --> 00:11:39.919
Aunt,

00:11:40.519 --> 00:11:42.519
Weilian and I bow to you.

