The couple bows to each other.

00:12:07.320 --> 00:12:09.440
Weilian, why aren't you bowing?

00:12:10.320 --> 00:12:11.879
You should be marrying me.

00:12:12.279 --> 00:12:12.799
Weilian,

00:12:13.639 --> 00:12:14.360
I'm the one

00:12:14.360 --> 00:12:15.200
you should be marrying!

00:12:15.679 --> 00:12:16.840
Get this crazy woman out of here!

00:12:16.960 --> 00:12:17.440
Weilian!

00:12:19.559 --> 00:12:20.879
You shouldn't treat her like that.

00:12:27.320 --> 00:12:29.279
Qingwan, let's continue the ceremony.

00:12:34.759 --> 00:12:35.840
You're regretting this.

00:12:38.039 --> 00:12:39.200
You're marrying me today,

00:12:40.279 --> 00:12:41.480
one way or another.

00:12:49.600 --> 00:12:49.960
Run!

00:12:50.559 --> 00:12:51.200
Run for it!

00:13:13.039 --> 00:13:13.759
Huo Xiu,

00:13:14.639 --> 00:13:15.960
how dare you crash my wedding!

00:13:17.360 --> 00:13:18.159
Why wouldn't I dare?

00:13:19.200 --> 00:13:21.120
I control all of Sucheng now.

00:13:22.320 --> 00:13:23.080
Why wouldn't I dare

00:13:24.840 --> 00:13:25.919
claim a woman?

00:13:33.759 --> 00:13:34.840
Give her back to me.

00:13:36.720 --> 00:13:37.399
Talk to me

00:13:38.039 --> 00:13:41.200
only if you leave here alive.

00:13:53.399 --> 00:13:56.840
You've even managed to buy the loyalty
of those around me.

00:13:58.840 --> 00:14:00.679
Money makes the mare go.

00:14:01.039 --> 00:14:02.480
Who can really refuse money?

00:14:02.840 --> 00:14:03.200
Right?

00:14:05.200 --> 00:14:06.100
If memory serves me right,

00:14:07.440 --> 00:14:08.679
you must despise him to the core by now.

00:14:12.639 --> 00:14:13.200
Of course.

00:14:14.720 --> 00:14:17.159
He killed my entire family.

00:14:18.639 --> 00:14:20.679
I'll end his life right here and now.

